data.description: Escape the city to this charming farmhouse with room to roam on nearly an acre of land. Numerous updates including new HVAC, flooring, appliances, fixtures, paint, and more. The main level includes a cosy living area, large kitchen, walk-in pantry, primary laundry room, 2 bedrooms, and a large covered patio. Upstairs, the master suite has an additional laundry hookup for stackable washer and dryer and has a private balcony with stunning views, while 2 additional bedrooms and a living area provide ample space. The property includes a spacious outbuilding or shop, is fenced, and is on county water. Unleash your creativity both inside and out in this country retreat.
